    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it garaged and pampered since day one, so it\u2019s in truly pristine condition inside and out. If you're looking for that 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
