    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system. The vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical refresh, including documented rod bearing replacement and a precise valve shim adjustment to ensure optimal valvetrain clearance. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement, mitigating common torsional stress issues. Power is delivered through a tactile six-speed Getrag manual gearbox to an M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing and suspension component remains within factory tolerances, preserving the car's legendary steering feedback and lateral stability. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44500.0,
